'''Broken Mirror''' ni filimi yo muri [[Gana]]  yasohotse muri 2014 ikozwe na  Media 5 Studio Productions<ref>BROKEN MIRROR | African Movie Review <nowiki>https://www.talkafricanmovies.com</nowiki> › broken-mirror</ref>. James Gardiner, Fred Amugi, Jackie Appiah, Roselyn Ngissah, Mikki Osei Berko, Victoria Lebene Mekpah na Jasmine Baroudi ni abakinnyi bingenzi<ref>BROKEN MIRROR - Media5promotions.com <nowiki>https://www.media5promotions.com</nowiki> › Featured</ref>. Yanditswe na Pappa Deric kandi yakozwe na David Owusu hamwe na Mikki Osei Berko nk'umuyobozi. Ninkuru yumugore uhinda umushyitsi mugihe amahirwe y'umukunzi we ahindutse neza, nyuma yo kumuhagararaho mubihe bikomeye<ref>BROKEN MIRROR - Media5promotions.com <nowiki>https://www.media5promotions.com</nowiki> › Featured</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Thompson yakinnye na James Gardiner, ni umunyeshuri urangije kaminuza udafite akazi ufata ububaji kugira ngo abeho<ref>Broken Mirror (film) and similar topics | Frankensaurus.com <nowiki>https://frankensaurus.com</nowiki> › Broken_Mirror_(film)</ref>. Umukunzi we Priscilla ( Jackie Appiah ) yamuhaye inkunga y'amarangamutima ndetse n'amafaranga<ref>Final Broken Mirror (DVD video, 2014) [WorldCat.org] <nowiki>https://www.worldcat.org</nowiki> › final-broken-mirror › oclc</ref>. Priscilla udakize kandi akora akazi ko kudoda, ahora ashimishwa na bagenzi be Evelyn (Roselyn Ngissah) na Angela (Victoria Lebene Mekpah) kubera urukundo rwe no gushyigikira byimazeyo Thompson<ref>james a thompson md - Opera News Ghana</ref>. Kumwizera kumutsindira mugihe cyImana birakomeye kandi arabikora mugihe cy'umwaka.<ref>Face of the Gods: The Artists and Their Altars - jstor <nowiki>https://www.jstor.org</nowiki> › stable</ref>

Barashyingirwa, barishima kandi bategereje umwana wabo wambere, mugihe Thompson yakiriye amashusho yerekana Priscilla nundi mugabo<ref>Broken Mirror - Letoyinspeak <nowiki>http://letoyinspeak.blogspot.com</nowiki> › 2014/10 › broken-m...</ref>. Ibi bimuha kumva ko ariganya kandi biganisha ku gusenyuka. Evelyn amenyesha umukunzi we Priscilla mugihe runaka. Hari ukuntu yemera ko Priscilla yamwibye kandi niwe uri ku mashusho hamwe na we<ref>Broken Mirror (2014) - nlist | Nollywood, Nigerian Movies ... <nowiki>https://nlist.ng</nowiki> › title › broken-mirror-476</ref>.
